{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act15d0_level_act15d0_04_end","storyGroup":"act15d0","storySort":9,"storyDependence":"act15d0_level_act15d0_04_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"MB-4","storyName":"勇敢，莽撞","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"赫默表达了自己的恐惧，对未知，对自己将要做的事的恐惧，而梅尔虽然无法安慰她，但至少为她提供了一时的勇气。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act15d0/level_act15d0_04_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act15d0_04","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":7,"next":9,"characters":["梅尔","赫默"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_bar_1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","id":6},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$nightoflongmen_intro","key":"$nightoflongmen_loop","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":10},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"所以，和卡夫卡的认识有什么问题吗？","id":11,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":12},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"不，不是和卡夫卡的认识有问题。而是......","id":13,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"和卡夫卡认识之后，我一直希望她能够过上正常的生活，不要再做以前那些见不得光的事情。","id":14,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我给她介绍了一些我能介绍的工作，甚至想要让她成为莱茵生命的一员，虽然最后失败了。","id":15,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但无论如何，我始终希望卡夫卡能够过上更好的生活，我希望她变好。而这个好，是以我在莱茵生命的生活作为标准的。","id":16,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"嗯......我觉得在莱茵生命的生活确实还不赖呀？","id":18,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"前提是我们不知道自己在做什么。","id":20,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#1","focus":"2","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"可是作为科研工作者，我们不是应该非常清楚自己在做什么吗？","id":22,"figure":"char_242_mayer#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#1","focus":"1","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"不，我不是指科研上的目的，而是那背后的东西。","id":24,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我们的研究如果真的成功会带来什么影响；我们的成果会被用来做什么；这是不是现在的我们应该研究的东西。","id":25,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"在“炎魔”之后，公司内部发生的一些事情让我开始考虑这个问题。","id":26,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我像你，像大部分同事一样，认为我们的研究是正确的，我们的方向是理想的。","id":27,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_242_mayer#1","focus":"1","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但真的是这样吗？","id":29,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"伊芙利特让我对这些事情产生了怀疑。","id":30,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这种怀疑促使我暂时离开了莱茵生命，前往了罗德岛。","id":31,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_242_mayer#1","focus":"2","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"原来赫默你一直在想这样的事情啊......","id":33,"figure":"char_242_mayer#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"在罗德岛的时间里，我一方面在进行科研工作，另一方面，我开始关注起过去没有在意过的一些数据。","id":35,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这些数据是老师给我的，我以前并不明白他将一些公司和地方的数据交给我是为了什么，我也都丢在了一边。","id":36,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但是随着对这些数据的分析和研究，我才发现了其中存在着各种各样的问题。","id":37,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"第一次发现其中问题的那一天，我彻夜未眠。","id":38,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"你是指和安东尼有关的事情吗？","id":40,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":41},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"不，安东尼，或者说西蒙公司的事只是其中一部分，甚至只是一小部分。","id":42,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"还有很多一样的事情在发生着，不只是在莱茵生命，是在哥伦比亚之中发生着。","id":43,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"那时我才真正意识到，我对莱茵生命这家公司，对哥伦比亚这个国家都了解得太少了。","id":44,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但我不甘心，我不觉得发生在伊芙利特身上的事，发生在安东尼身上的事应该是正常的。","id":45,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"所以我才会想要插手安东尼这件事。","id":46,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但是，我或许步子迈得太大了。","id":47,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我现在的感觉和那一天一样，塞雷娅从试验场地将昏迷的伊芙利特抱出来时，仿佛被人从头浇了一盆冰水。","id":48,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#1","focus":"2","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"那次实验究竟发生了什么？","id":50,"figure":"char_242_mayer#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#1","focus":"1","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我不知道。","id":52,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":53},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"诶？","id":54,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我一直以为我知道我在做什么，但我现在才发现，我其实不知道。","id":56,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我只知道，我绝不能让伊芙利特再被那样对待。","id":57,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这可能，是我现在唯一能够坚持的事情了。","id":58,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#1","focus":"2","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"......赫默，你有些醉了，我去给你倒点醒酒茶吧。","id":60,"figure":"char_242_mayer#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"嗯......","id":62,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialog","id":63},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","id":64},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.8","id":65},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":66},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"50","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":67},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_empty","id":68},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":69},{"type":"Character","name":"char_242_mayer#1","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"对不起，赫默，我不知道怎么安慰你。","id":71,"figure":"char_242_mayer#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#1","id":72},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这不怪你，梅尔。","id":73,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我只怪我自己过去太无知了。","id":75,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_242_mayer#2","id":76},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"我觉得赫默你已经知道得很多了，只是大家都有不擅长的领域。","id":77,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","id":78},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但是，梅尔，我是真的不甘心。","id":79,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"如果我能知道得更多一些，如果我能知道得更早一些，或许事情不会变成现在这样。","id":80,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_242_mayer#2","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"但是现在开始知道也来得及呀。","id":82,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"我觉得缪尔赛思主任应该也觉得你挺厉害的。","id":83,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"我说实话哦，赫默。","id":84,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"你说。","id":86,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_242_mayer#2","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"我感觉赫默你现在有些像我一些同事。","id":88,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"就是在知道了一些新的知识后，就觉得自己过去学的一点用都没有，然后开始哀叹自己为什么没有早点遇上这门学问。","id":89,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"不是说这样就不对啦，但是我觉得这样就很没意思，难道以前努力过的东西真的就没用了吗？新的东西就一定好吗？","id":90,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"如果它真的好，如果真的觉得它有用，那么用和以前一样的努力去学习它不就好了，没有什么好着急的。","id":91,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":92},{"type":"Character","id":93},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":94},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_empty","id":95},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"50","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":96},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":97},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":98},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-50","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":99},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","id":100},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":101},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"来，喝了这杯醒酒茶。","id":103,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"不是你说的那样，这些事情和学问不一样......","id":105,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但是，但是你说的也有道理，确实......","id":106,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"哎呀，算了，我来喂你喝吧，真是的，赫默你酒量不行呀。","id":108,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":109},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","id":110},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":111},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":112},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-80","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":113},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"梅尔将几近趴在桌子上的赫默扶了起来，一点一点把醒酒茶喂进了她的嘴里。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"900","id":114},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":115},{"type":"Subtitle","id":116},{"type":"Dialog","id":117},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":118},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":119},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"80","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":120},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":121},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":122},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"怎么样，感觉好点没？","id":123,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"嘶......呼......","id":125,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#1","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"好多了，谢谢你，梅尔。","id":127,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#1","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"要是你感觉不好受的话，要不然我们直接回去吧？","id":129,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":130},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......不，还不到那个时候。","id":131,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":132},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"你还要继续和缪尔赛思主任聊天吗？","id":133,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":134},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"嗯。","id":135,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"不愧是赫默，这么快就调整好了心态。","id":137,"figure":"char_242_mayer#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......其实完全没有。","id":139,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","id":140},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"虽然我也很想就这么逃开，现在立刻回去。","id":141,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但是这次机会很难得，即使我再难受，我也必须要坚持到最后。","id":142,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"你刚才说的话，虽然无法解决我现在的问题，不过有一点我认为很对。","id":143,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我只能用和以前一样的努力去学习和接受这些新的“知识”。","id":144,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"不过，我也要做一些额外的准备。","id":145,"figure":"char_108_silent_1#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":146},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":147},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":148},{"type":"Character","id":149},{"type":"Image","id":150}],"characters":["梅尔","赫默"]}